{"tid":1697833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玻利維亞土著總統黑箱灌票，人民在最高選舉法院前焚燒票箱","createTime":"2019-11-07T05:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T13:15:43.000Z","uid":62011,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7b823f2273b6c4a822212c5a864f0445b60484c4","tid":1697833,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:51:01.000Z","msg":"怒火燒到玻利維亞。2016年無視限制任期公投的土著總統莫拉萊斯，謀取第三度連任，投票結果本來顯示他以45%領先對手梅薩的38%。由於差距不足10%，意味需要進入第二輪投票。然而這個時候，點票網站停止更新24小時才重啟，差距突變10.12%，莫拉萊斯當選。人民怒轟黑箱灌票，在最高選舉法院前<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">焚燒票箱</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-50134451?fbclid=IwAR104cQgJgRipmqnDu7UR7KZHlAr-26mCQCmpL1NXXTr3MU8DsagMERt0dY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-50134451%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR104cQgJgRipmqnDu7UR7KZHlAr-26mCQCmpL1NXXTr3MU8DsagMERt0dY&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=e32a43fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-50134451%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR104cQgJgRipmqnDu7UR7KZHlAr-26mCQCmpL1NXXTr3MU8DsagMERt0dY&h=48cdbdf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-50134451?fbclid=IwAR104cQgJgRipmqnDu7UR7KZHlAr-26mCQCmpL1NXXTr3MU8DsagMERt0dY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hxn71YW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxn71YW.png&h=7c25ff95&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n涉改裝雨傘 15 歲男童兩罪罪成 裁判官：雷射筆本身非攻擊性武器 但被告有意圖照射警<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E6%94%B9%E8%A3%9D%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98-15-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E9%9D%9E%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2582%2598-15-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=f153bb99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2582%2598-15-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&h=b45d3af3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E6%94%B9%E8%A3%9D%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98-15-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E9%9D%9E%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/</a><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n唔敢承認法治已死，又唔敢燒法院。燒下個法律女神(雕塑)。上下國際新聞，等人知道香港法治 已死。"},{"pid":"bb280f8febc235d8351bb30aa8ec07380123eb7f","tid":1697833,"uid":13474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvCTcoV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvCTcoV.jpg&h=87c59ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樽頸突破！11 11 黎明行動 7:00 18區集合 行動強制罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.k